casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2281. Resolution Trust Corp. v. J.B. Centron Dev. Co., Inc.

Lucas County, No. L-92-206. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective May 5, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
